title: Elanguides CFA level 2 notes
description:
Hi guys,
Elanguides CFA Level 2 notes is in da house.

although this is not the latest version (this is 2012 version to be precise), it still covers 85-90% of the main content in today's CFA curriculum. So if you're fed up with Schweser and are really into Elan, this is it.

Remember to check year-to-year LOS changes provided free by Elanguides.com, so you know which part to read, and which to ignore from this 2012 version.

Note there are individual subject notes that are provided free on elanguides.com as part of their endorsement such as Econ and Quant material.

Enjoy, and leave some feedback!
